snippet.title: EatTheBlocks
snippet.description:
AIRDROP UNTIL APRIL 30th (EAT THE BLOCKS TOKEN)
👉 Register for the airdrop: https://mailchi.mp/eattheblocks/airdrop
👉 This token will allow you to vote on the content of the channel, plus other features announced later
👉 Address of the token: 0x7AC64008FA000BfDc4494e0BfCC9F4efF3d51d2a
👉 Page of token on Bscscan: https://bscscan.com/address/0x7ac64008fa000bfdc4494e0bfcc9f4eff3d51d2a

Do you want to learn how to build Solidity smart contracts and Ethereum decentralized applications (Dapps)? 

On this channel, you will find a ton of high-quality tutorials on Solidity and Ethereum Dapps development:
- How to learn Solidity programming?
- How to develop Ethereum smart contracts?
- How to build decentralized applications (Dapps) on Ethereum?
- How to use the Truffle framework / Ganache for Dapp development?
- How to use Web3 to interact with a smart contract?

If you want access to more tutorials, check out my private website with even more videos / advanced topics: pro.eattheblocks.com
